public abstract class BaseSet<Value> extends BaseCollection<Value> implements com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Copyable<Value,BaseSet<Value>>, Set<Value>
A set with a maximum size. Adds useful methods to the usual Set operations, as well as implementing:

  • Sequence

  • Countable
  • Joinable
  • StringFormattable
